title: Poser ~ DAZ3D : 1949 Pontiac Convertible [RO 95646]
description:
This is a Poser figure representing a car inspired in the 1949 Pontiac Silver Streak

 You can open the left, right and back door, turn and move the wheels. 

 You get with the product, the car itself , the HQ textures you can see in the sample images and the texture templates.

 Some car materials have a raytrace node in the refrect, you need to check the raytrace Box in your Poser render settings.

 To get the car refrect like in the sample images. you put something near the car, a prop, another car or somethig it will be refrected in the car automatically.

 Change the Reflect value to get more or less reflection in the material room.

 All the samples images are rendered in Poser.
